1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,910
[Episode 47]

2
00:00:04,550 --> 00:00:13,350
I won't ask if you're okay
Because you clearly aren't

3
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,110
Are you some kind of stalker?
How do you manage to follow me everywhere?

4
00:00:21,650 --> 00:00:29,130
I've been following since the bar
I saw what happened at the hotel too

5
00:00:33,910 --> 00:00:43,470
I don't know if I did that
to make Fuzhi happy

6
00:00:45,590 --> 00:00:51,950
Or to make myself
feel less guilty toward him

7
00:01:00,910 --> 00:01:10,690
Didn't I tell you?
Couples who don't sleep together won't last

8
00:01:19,110 --> 00:01:22,210
It's quite ironic though

9
00:01:25,510 --> 00:01:27,990
This thing called love

10
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:36,810
Is like a candle
Once the wax burns out, it goes out

11
00:01:42,450 --> 00:01:49,270
But strangely, whenever I need to go somewhere
Fuzhi always drives me

12
00:01:49,910 --> 00:01:54,270
He sits there waiting for hours
Without a single complaint

13
00:01:58,509 --> 00:02:00,210
So I really don't know

14
00:02:00,210 --> 00:02:08,910
If he does that because he loves me
Or because he doesn't care about me at all

15
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,630
I don't know

16
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:37,530
Because for me, love is possession

17
00:02:39,329 --> 00:02:48,270
Becoming the owner
I don't care if anyone calls me selfish

18
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:53,370
But I absolutely won't accept
The person I love fooling around with others

19
00:02:55,970 --> 00:03:01,530
I also won't allow
Anyone else to touch the person I love

20
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:12,450
Because the person I love
Must belong only to me

21
00:03:14,950 --> 00:03:20,030
No one else has any right

22
00:03:51,829 --> 00:03:54,630
[To Be Continued]
